---
title: Chipotle Beef Couscous Bowl with Sweetcorn and Soured Cream
description: Ready in less than 15 minutes, this Super Quick Chipotle Beef Couscous Bowl is spicy and delicious. The main flavour here comes from chipotle, full of rich, smoky and fruity flavours with a kick from the chipotle chillies.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R08_W29_UK_UQ17517-8_MAIN_low-2c172431.jpg
